These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
House: futuristic, wooden, modern, gothic-revival
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, cherry, apple, peach
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, lavender, white, amber
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person who likes lavender is the person eating peach##1
2. the person who likes white is between the modern house and the gothic-revival house##2
3. the person who likes lavender is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the person driving the tram is the modern house##1
7. the person eating cherry is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
9. the wooden house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| House   | wooden | gothic-revival   | futuristic  | modern  |
| Food   | cherry    | peach    | nectarine      | apple    |
| Color   | amber | lavender | white | mauve |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

