.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, september, may
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, poppy, lily
4 different games are played: go, domino, snooker, bridge
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
3. the person playing bridge is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who growslily is between the person playing snooker and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who growslily and the person playing bridge##2
7. the person playing go is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | may | june    | september  | april    |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | daisy  | lily  | poppy |
| Game           | bridge      | snooker       | domino      | go       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

