.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, dutch, german, argentine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, reggae, jazz, punk
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, soy-milk, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the german is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
6. the person drinking juice is the fan of punk##1
7. the argentine is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the nigerian is between the fan of d&b and the fan of punk##2
9. the fan of jazz is between the german and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality        | dutch | german     | nigerian   | argentine     |
| Music-Genre       | reggae   | d&b   | jazz | punk |
| Beverage         | water   | soy-milk | coffee       | juice    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

