.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, aconite, balloon-flower
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, subway, roller
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, mexican, turkish
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the roller is the person who growsbellflower##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the turkish##1
 4. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the roller is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the pakistani##1
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the indonesian##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is between the owner of the bird and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Flower           | bellflower  | balloon-flower | marigold     | aconite |
| Transport   | roller | bike  | subway | quad-bike       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Nationality         | pakistani | indonesian   | turkish   | mexican         |

