.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
City: colone, prague, berlin, london
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, december, august
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, american, italian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is the person traveling to prague##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the japanese is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the japanese##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the american##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the australian##2
10. the italian is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| City          | prague         | berlin         | colone     | london      |
| Birthday           | december | august | february    | april     |
| Nationality   | australian      | italian       | japanese    | american       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

