 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is the fan of house##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
